==Scottish Gaelic==

===Noun===
'''bòrd''' {{m}}, '''bùird''' {{p}}

# [[table]]
#* air a' bòrd
#** on the table
#* aig bòrd
#** at table
# [[plank]], [[board]]
# [[board]] (directors or managers of a company)
# [[food]]
#* a bhòrd 's a leabaidh
#** his board and bed
# bank edge
#* bòrd an loch
#** bank of the lake

===Verb===
'''bòrd'''
# [[tack]] (in sailing)
# [[board]] (as a ship)
#* bhord iad an long
#** they boarded the ship

